  "title": "🧋🍿 x10 RETAIL ASSISTANTS (TEA & SNACKS KIOSK) | $12+ PER HOUR | INCENTIVES | 5 DAY WORK 🍭🥤",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for F&B Retail staff to join our client's beverage and snacks kiosk across their outlets island-wide!</p><p><strong>Hiring Locations: </strong>Chinatown/Ang Mo Kio/Pasir Ris</p><h3><strong>💰 Salary & Perks</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>$12 per hour 💰</strong></li><li><strong>Public Holiday = Double Pay 🎉</strong></li><li><strong>Staff Incentives:</strong> Bi-weekly 💰</li><li><strong>Daily staff treat:</strong> 1 complimentary bag of snacks 🎉</li></ul><h3><strong>🧋 What You’ll Do:</strong></h3><ul><li>Preparing and serving a variety of tea drinks and beverages</li><li>Assisting with light snacks testing and packing</li><li>Keeping the workspace clean, organised, and food-safe</li><li>Use and maintain tea-brewing equipment</li><li>Handling customer orders and basic cash transactions</li></ul><h3><strong>⏰ Working Hours</strong></h3><p><strong>5-day work week</strong> (<strong>minimum 30 hours/week</strong>, 6 hours/day)<br />Shifts are rostered and may rotate:<br /><strong>A:</strong> 9:00am – 3:00pm<br /><strong>B:</strong> 11:00am – 5:00pm<br /><strong>C:</strong> 4:30pm – 10:30pm<br /><strong>No break time</strong><br /><strong>At least 2 weekend days off each month</strong><br />Hours may adjust based on operational needs</p><h3><strong>What You Bring:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Food Safety Level 1 Certification</strong> (required when you start work)</li><li>Previous similar experience is a plus, If no experience training will be provided!</li></ul><p>*</p><p>Shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p>*</p><p>Jeremiah Lim (R22106910)</p><p>CREW by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd </p><p>EA24C2435</p>",
